<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Privacy & Security | KisanVikas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .policy-page {
            max-width: 1250px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0 4%;
        }

        .policy-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 45px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(30, 92, 55, 0.06);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .policy-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .policy-card h2 {
            color: #123b22;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .policy-card h2::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e5c37, #3cab6b);
            margin: 10px auto 20px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .policy-card h3 {
            color: #1e5c37;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-card p {
            color: #587060;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .policy-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .policy-card ul li {
            padding: 6px 0 6px 22px;
            position: relative;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        .policy-card ul li::before {
            content: '•';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #2ecc71;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .policy-card strong {
            color: #1a7a3a;
        }

        .updated-date {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-left">
            <p>Email: support@agriculture.com</p>
            <p>Toll-Free: 1800-123-4567</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-center">
            <h1>KisanVikas</h1>
            <p>Empowering Farmers, Ensuring Growth</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <a href="/profile">
                <img src="/Assets/woman.png" alt="Profile" class="profile-pic">
            </a>
            {{#if currentUser}}
            <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">Logout</a>
            {{else}}
            <a href="/" class="logout-btn">Login</a>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/Assets/K1.png" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="menu-toggle" id="mobile-menu">☰</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/index">Home</a>
            <div class="dropdown">
                <a href="#" class="dropdown-btn">Services</a>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/schemes">Schemes</a>
                    <a href="/crop">Crop Guidance</a>
                    <a href="/loan">Loan Calculator</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/schemes">Schemes</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="policy-page">
        <div class="policy-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt" style="color:#2ecc71;margin-right:8px"></i>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="updated-date">Last updated: April 11, 2025</p>
            <p>At KisanVikas, we value and respect your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect
                your information.</p>

            <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal Information (Name, Email, Phone Number)</li>
                <li>Device Information (IP address, Browser type)</li>
                <li>Usage Data (Pages visited, Time spent)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
                <li>To communicate important updates or offers</li>
                <li>To respond to your queries or requests</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Information Sharing</h3>
            <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties, except when required by law.
            </p>

            <h3>Cookies</h3>
            <p>We use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze website traffic. You can manage your cookie
                preferences through your browser settings.</p>

            <h3>Your Rights</h3>
            <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us
                at <strong>help@kisanvikas.com</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-lock" style="color:#f0c040;margin-right:8px"></i>Security Information</h2>
            <p>Protecting your data is our top priority.</p>

            <h3>Data Encryption</h3>
            <p>All sensitive information is encrypted during transmission and storage to protect against unauthorized
                access.</p>

            <h3>Secure Authentication</h3>
            <p>Our platform uses secure login methods with password hashing to verify users and prevent unauthorized
                access.</p>

            <h3>Regular Updates</h3>
            <p>We regularly update our systems and monitor for vulnerabilities to maintain a secure environment.</p>

            <h3>Your Responsibilities</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Keep your login credentials confidential.</li>
                <li>Report any suspicious activity immediately to <strong>security@kisanvikas.com</strong>.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer id="modern-footer">
        <div class="modern-footer-container">
            <div class="footer-column-footer-logo">
                <img src="/Assets/K1.png" alt="Logo">
                <p>Your trusted partner for digital solutions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-column">
                <h2>Follow Us</h2>
                <div class="modern-footer-icons">
                    <a href="#"><img src="/Assets/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
                    <a href="#"><img src="/Assets/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                    <a href="#"><img src="/Assets/instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                    <a href="#"><img src="/Assets/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-column">
                <h2>Quick Links</h2>
                <ul class="modern-footer-links">
                    <li><a href="/index">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/loan">Loan Calculator</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/schemes">Schemes</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/crop">Crop Guidance</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-column">
                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <ul class="modern-footer-contact">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> PCCOE, Pune</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Toll-Free: 1800-123-4567</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> support@agriculture.com</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> <a href="https://forms.gle/E5sQEWYuMW8FFmyN9">Give
                            Feedback</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modern-footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2025 KisanVikas | <a href="/policy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        const mobileMenu = document.getElementById("mobile-menu");
        if (mobileMenu) {
            mobileMenu.addEventListener("click", function () {
                document.querySelector(".nav-links").classList.toggle("active");
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>